data.title: Beer List — YIA YIA'S
data.text:
TAP BEER

UP TO 25 TAPS

We (currently) feature up to 25 rotating beers on tap. You can keep updated on tap beers, ales & styles as they change by scrolling down and clicking “On Tap - Downtown or On Tap - Van Dorn.” follow us on Facebook, Twitter or Instagram for weekly specials.

BOTTLED BEER

LARGE VARIETY OF BEERS, ALES & STYLES

We have one of Lincoln’s largest bottle selections with over 160 craft beers from around the world. Watch for new and seasonal additions by following us on Untappd.com, Facebook, Twitter or Instagram.
